  ],
  "remarks": "Karoon Oil & Gas Production Company is Iran’s largest oil production company and a subsidiary of the National Iranian Oil Company (NIOC). The National Iranian Oil Company (NIOC) is a State-owned and operated entity providing substantial financial resources to the Government of Iran. NIOC holds the production, sale and export monopoly for Iranian oil. The revenue generated by NIOC’s oil sales plays a significant role in funding Iran’s military and the IRGC.",
